Gwyddion the Druid is here ready to help any wayward Mages.
~
Gwyddion the Druid sits here with his herbs and potions. Healing 
the wounds of any hurt Mage. If you're lucky he might tell you a 
story of his adventures long ago. But for now you feel safe in 
the aura that surrounds him.
