#16403
Hall of Death~
Hooks to hang bags filled to the brim line the walls. You see a cloak 
that has turned to stone and is now part of the black marble wall. No 
doubt from a spell gone wrong. This is not the kind of place you want 
to come to very often unless you need to. Mages come here to chant arcane
words from their spell books.  But the screams of the dead pervade this room 
with their presence.  Only the strong may enter here and leave alive...
~
