#16404
Hall of Learning~
The place for Mages to learn and practice their spells, thus making 
them stronger. There is a place to put their bags of books, a desk over 
in the corner for writing a spell if they need to. A bunch of mats a lined 
neatly in a row, allowing the Mage to sit so as not to get weary from 
chanting spells endlessly.
~
