#16405
Hall of Training~
As you enter the room, you see dark marble pillars lining each wall. 
Dark leather fighting mats are stacked in piles along the wall ready 
for use. A small rack has swords and shields in it. You think you can 
hear the clanging of swords long ago when the great Mages of lore 
trained here.
~
