#16407
Hall of the Dead~
As soon as you enter the room the foul smell of rotting flesh 
overwhelms you.  You realize this is not a place where you should be.  
There are many corpses laying on the ground in many different stages of decay.  
You look down at your feet and find hundreds of maggots covered in blood 
crawling on you.  They seem to be looking for fresh meat.  You hear a metallic 
sound and look up in time to see an executioner's axe come crashing 
down on your neck.
~
