#16409
#pShadow of a Whisper#n~
Your soul seems to elevate within the embrace of the gentle 
breeze that blows against your skin. Shadows dance on the 
walls, as if puppeted by some unseen force, filling your mind 
with a sense of someone occupying the room with you. Whispers 
fill the room, those of children, and others who have occupied 
the room before you, sharing the laughter and happiness which 
call this room home. In the corner a single chair sits facing 
the only window that adorns the walls, the sunlight gently 
touching the fabric with its fingertips. Adorning the other 
walls are portraits of all the archmages, who share the 
friendship with Siervua, each staring down on you.
~
